---
title: Cheesy Chorizo Tex-Mex Orzo Skillet with Tortilla Crumble and Sour Cream
description: Say hello to this satisfying meal, full of flavour and heartiness, a fiesta for the taste buds! Ground chorizo is cooked with a zesty Mexican seasoning before being finished in a skillet with orzo, sweet peppers and cheesy tortilla crumble topper.
